# Rule: Document Organization (One Idea = One Full Doc Set)

> Enforce consistent document organization: one idea = one complete set of discovery + validation docs

## Core Principle

**Every idea must have a complete, organized document set. All discovery docs go in `/docs/discovery/`. All validation docs go in `/docs/validation/`. All documents for an idea share the same `<idea-slug>` identifier.**

## Document Structure

### Discovery Documents (`/docs/discovery/`)

**All discovery documents for an idea must be in `/docs/discovery/` with consistent naming:**

- `NARRATIVE-<idea-slug>.md` - Manus narrative output (raw)
- `NICHE-INTEL-<idea-slug>.md` - Niche Intelligence analysis
- `PAIN-SIGNALS-<idea-slug>.md` - Pain Signal analysis
- `JTBD-<idea-slug>.md` - Persona & JTBD analysis
- `OPPORTUNITY-<idea-slug>.md` - Opportunity & Moat analysis
- `REDTEAM-<idea-slug>.md` - Red-Team critique (optional)

**Example**: For idea "enterprise-design-system-startups":
- `/docs/discovery/NARRATIVE-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/discovery/NICHE-INTEL-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/discovery/PAIN-SIGNALS-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/discovery/JTBD-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/discovery/OPPORTUNITY-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/discovery/REDTEAM-enterprise-design-system-startups.md` (optional)

### Validation Documents (`/docs/validation/`)

**All validation documents for an idea must be in `/docs/validation/` with consistent naming:**

- `VALIDATION-PLAN-<idea-slug>.md` - Validation plan with tests and thresholds
- `LANDING-<idea-slug>.md` - Landing page copy and visuals
- `DISTRIBUTION-<idea-slug>.md` - Distribution strategy
- `PRICING-TEST-<idea-slug>.md` - Pricing test strategy
- `CREATIVE-BATCH-<idea-slug>.md` - Creative batch workflows (Glif)
- `RESULTS-<idea-slug>.md` - Validation test results
- `REDTEAM-<idea-slug>.md` - Red-Team critique (optional)

**Example**: For idea "enterprise-design-system-startups":
- `/docs/validation/VALIDATION-PLAN-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/validation/LANDING-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/validation/DISTRIBUTION-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/validation/PRICING-TEST-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/validation/CREATIVE-BATCH-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/validation/RESULTS-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/validation/REDTEAM-enterprise-design-system-startups.md` (optional)

### Automation Specs (`/docs/automation/lindy/`)

**All Lindy automation specs must be in `/docs/automation/lindy/` with consistent naming:**

- `LINDY-SPEC-<automation-name>-<idea-slug>.md` - Lindy automation spec

**Example**: For idea "enterprise-design-system-startups":
- `/docs/automation/lindy/LINDY-SPEC-WAITLIST-NURTURE-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/automation/lindy/LINDY-SPEC-OUTREACH-SEQUENCER-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`
- `/docs/automation/lindy/LINDY-SPEC-DAILY-BRIEF-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`

## Idea Slug Requirements

**Idea slugs must be:**
- Lowercase
- Hyphenated (no spaces, underscores, or special characters)
- Descriptive but concise (e.g., `enterprise-design-system-startups`, not `eds` or `enterprise_design_system`)
- Consistent across all documents for the same idea

**Examples**:
- ✅ `enterprise-design-system-startups`
- ✅ `real-estate-investor-flipper-platform`
- ✅ `ai-code-review-documentation-tool`
- ❌ `Enterprise Design System` (uppercase, spaces)
- ❌ `enterprise_design_system` (underscores)
- ❌ `eds` (too short, not descriptive)

