## Quality Gates

**All document sets must pass quality gates:**

- ✅ **All discovery docs use same `<idea-slug>`**
- ✅ **All validation docs use same `<idea-slug>`**
- ✅ **All docs in correct folders** (`/docs/discovery/` or `/docs/validation/`)
- ✅ **Idea slug is lowercase, hyphenated, descriptive**
- ✅ **No orphaned documents** (all docs for an idea are present)

## Document Set Completeness

**A complete discovery doc set includes:**
- NARRATIVE (from Manus)
- NICHE-INTEL
- PAIN-SIGNALS
- JTBD
- OPPORTUNITY
- REDTEAM (optional but recommended)

**A complete validation doc set includes:**
- VALIDATION-PLAN
- LANDING
- DISTRIBUTION
- PRICING-TEST
- CREATIVE-BATCH
- RESULTS (after tests run)
- REDTEAM (optional but recommended)

